graph LR
    KServe[KServe Platform<br/>serving.kserve.io]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KServe -->|serverless autoscaling<br/>scale-to-zero<br/>CRD: serving.knative.dev| Knative[Knative Serving 1.x<br/>REQUIRED]
    KServe -->|traffic routing<br/>mTLS service mesh<br/>CRD: networking.istio.io| Istio[Istio 1.x<br/>REQUIRED]
    KServe -->|TLS certificates<br/>webhook server certs<br/>CRD: cert-manager.io| CertManager[cert-manager 1.x<br/>REQUIRED]
    KServe -->|container orchestration<br/>CRD API server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS| K8s[Kubernetes 1.23+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    KServe -.->|metrics scraping<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>/metrics endpoint| Prometheus[Prometheus 2.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
    KServe -.->|CloudEvents logging<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS| KnativeEventing[Knative Eventing<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    KServe -->|CRD sharing<br/>alternative serving<br/>high-density mode| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving<br/>Internal ODH]
    KServe -->|model registry<br/>metadata integration<br/>deployment orchestration| ODHModelController[ODH Model Controller<br/>Internal ODH]
    KServe -.->|OAuth2/OIDC authz<br/>Istio AuthorizationPolicy<br/>inference endpoint auth| Authorino[Authorino<br/>Internal ODH<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Integration Points (Consumers)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Internal ODH] -->|UI management<br/>InferenceService CRUD<br/>Kubernetes API| KServe
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Internal ODH] -->|auto-deploy models<br/>pipeline outputs<br/>Kubernetes API| KServe

    %% External Services (Storage)
    KServe -->|model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>AWS SigV4 auth| S3[S3 Storage<br/>AWS/Minio/Ceph]
    KServe -->|model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>GCP SA auth| GCS[Google Cloud Storage]
    KServe -->|model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Azure creds auth| Azure[Azure Blob Storage]
    KServe -->|model metadata<br/>download URIs<br/>HTTP/gRPC API| ModelRegistry[External Model Registry<br/>MLflow/Seldon]

    %% Dependency on Kubernetes Resources
    K8s -.->|provides| CoreResources[Core Resources<br/>Deployments<br/>Services<br/>ConfigMaps<br/>Secrets]
    K8s -.->|provides| CRDSupport[CRD Support<br/>CustomResourceDefinition<br/>API extensions]
    K8s -.->|provides| RBAC[RBAC<br/>ClusterRoles<br/>RoleBindings<br/>ServiceAccounts]

    KServe -->|creates/manages| CoreResources
    KServe -->|defines| CRDSupport
    KServe -->|uses| RBAC

